{
  "name": "Breath of Enoki Invasive",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest medical chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The medical chakra begins to cause your weapon to glow with a soft pink hue.</p><p>You fire a single attack into the ground or space your target is in, releasing a powerful burst of poisonous fumes to weaken them further.</p><p>Select a space you can see within range. All creatures within 10 feet of the chosen space must make a constitution saving throw.   depending on the severity of their failure, the poison does increasingly more things.</p><p>● Failed by 1~4: 5d6 poison damage and 1 ranks of corroded.<br />● Failed by 5~9: 5d6 poison damage and 2 rank of corroded.</p><p>● Failed by 10~14: 5d6 poison damage, 2 ranks of corroded, and 1 rank of envenomed.</p><p>● Failed by 15+: 5d6 poison damage, 2 ranks of corroded, and 2 rank of envenomed. </p>",
